Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.24,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,С чем ты там согласна?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.17,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,Пред.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.31,0:08:05.35,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,Aren't you guys hot? Вам разве не жарко?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:12.21,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,What? Чего?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:17.10,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,We said we'd all change our\N uniforms at the same time! Мы же договаривались поменять форму одновременно!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.39,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,We did? Правда?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.56,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,We did! You jumped the gun! Правда!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:25.86,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,I see. Сука
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:31.07,Next day,Text,0,0,0,,На следующий день
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:37.75,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,It's a lot cooler wearing short sleeves! Так и знала, так намного прохладнее
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.49,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:43.03,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,You guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.03,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Санаэ-тян,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.73,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,доброго утре… чка…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:58.02,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0,0,0,,I thought you said we were all \Ngonna switch together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.44,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Я забыла тебе сказать.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.27,0:09:12.92,Main-Mina,Мина,0,0,0,,Legf fe hogh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.55,0:09:18.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,"English Translation."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.64,0:09:20.96,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:26.06,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Walk down this street to the\N post office and turn left there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.87,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,You will see the station.\N It takes five minutes from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.78,0:09:34.88,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to get back at Такаги-сан today somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:38.64,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the best way to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.73,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't made a jack-in-the-box in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, I don't have enough materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.58,0:09:48.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Besides, it won't be finished\N in time if I start making it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.44,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,All right, let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.32,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:56.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.99,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Don't "Huh? Yes, sir" me. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.69,0:10:06.07,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It's sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.48,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,It's sixteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.57,0:10:16.07,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,This isn't math class. It's English!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:18.12,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I told you to translate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:20.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.71,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Never mind. Sit back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I even told you\N we're on line sixteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did she intentionally tell me\N that so I'd get it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.21,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I didn't think you'd {\i1}actually{\i0} get it wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:39.62,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Something on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:43.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:53.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.63,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,were you thinking of something naughty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:00.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:02.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.59,0:11:04.93,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.06,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:08.93,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:13.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You were actually thinking how to\N get back at me for all the teasing I do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I-I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I guessed right, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.82,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You were looking my way, so I kind of figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:26.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,If you knew, then don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.22,0:11:30.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It's fun to see your reactions, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:33.38,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,And? Did you come up with any good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:39.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Yeah, I did. I came up with the perfect plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,It's foolproof.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:47.26,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's not worried at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can she see into my mind\N and realize I don't have a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,So? What's the plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:58.07,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,A-As if I'd tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Just a hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.71,0:12:02.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No… Anyway, we should\N be paying attention to cla—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.87,June 18th,Board,0,0,0,,June 18th
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.73,0:12:05.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today is the eighteenth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:09.33,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Такаги-сан's student\N number is eighteen as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.46,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I keep Такаги-сан's\N attention away from class,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:15.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}she might get in trouble for\Nnot knowing where we are in the textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.54,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:20.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,what did you eat for breakfast today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:25.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Mountain yam over rice. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.73,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No reason in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.19,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,So… you like mountain yams?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.62,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Yeah, I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.26,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I feel energized the entire day\N when I eat them in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:39.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I kinda get what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.61,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,What about you, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Me? I…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:50.44,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.73,0:12:52.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "rice"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:56.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I didn't peg you as someone\N who eats bread. Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:58.88,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No, I did eat rice, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:02.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's working! Keep her attention\N away from class!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.83,0:13:04.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан, you prefer rice, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:07.59,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,I want someone to read from\N the top of the next page.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.59,0:13:10.43,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hmm… Today is the eighteenth, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:11.63,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Такаги.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.51,0:13:13.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well? You don't know where we are, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I will not do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.61,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.11,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.68,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:35.60,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn, she's good. I wouldn't expect\N anything less from Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to come up with another plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:45.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I should go on a direct\N attack with a jack-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:49.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, again,\N I don't have the materials!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.04,0:13:53.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката, what's troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,U-Uh… it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:14:00.19,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Were you thinking about me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:05.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't put it that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:10.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Besides, why would I be thinking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.25,0:14:12.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Then you were thinking\N about something naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.06,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No, I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:21.85,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I'm always thinking about you, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.93,0:14:27.00,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:35.35,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You're just thinking about teasing me\Nlike just now, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:43.94,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:50.36,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was that… momentary silence just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:53.14,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Today is June eighteenth,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:57.17,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,and if I add the month and date\N together, it's 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:58.37,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Number 24, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:04.88,Pool,Title,0,0,0,,Pool
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:03.20,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,"Pool."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:15.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the first day we get to go in\N the pool, but all I can do is watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:20.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it weren't for this injured hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:27.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No fair. They're all having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:28.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,It's the first day of swimming,\N and all we can do is watch. It's sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:36.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,T-Такаги-сан, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:37.29,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.83,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,In your case, is it because\N of your hand? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:45.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:48.39,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You know, things happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:52.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I bet you tried to pet a stray cat\N and got bitten, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,How did you know?! I didn't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:00.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I'm actually right?! I just took a wild guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.18,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,What a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:10.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Why are you just observing today—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That reminds me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:21.82,Main,Takao,0,0,0,,A girl who sits out swimming lessons\N is usually on her period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.82,0:16:25.63,Main,Takao,0,0,0,,According to the textbook,\N it causes abdominal pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.93,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what the King of Health Class, Takao, said…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:32.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I shouldn't. I don't think it's something\N I should be asking, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.53,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You wanted to ask why I'm not swimming today?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.56,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}She heard me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:47.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Well, I figured out your reason\N is your injured hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,so why don't you try to guess my reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-Not feeling good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.98,0:16:57.28,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,That's too vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.31,0:17:01.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,No, forget it. I don't really wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:04.37,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Then I guess I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,All right, I'll take a guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You get one try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:14.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Though I don't think you can guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:17.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn Такаги-сан…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:20.60,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she confident because\N she thinks I can't say "period"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case, she's seriously mocking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:24.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:27.48,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Такаги-сан we're talking about.\N It could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:33.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\an8\i1}Even if I gathered my courage and answered…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.42,0:17:32.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,"Period!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.18,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,No, you're so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:40.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's very likely!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:42.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}But knowing Такаги-сан,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:48.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}she probably already knows what\N I'm thinking and why I'm hesitating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:51.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then she'll counter that with…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.31,0:17:57.97,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You don't even know the reason\N why a girl isn't swimming?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.17,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I win, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.35,0:18:03.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it a trap or an honest question?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.34,0:18:05.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she making it seem genuine\N so I'll fall into her trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or is she making it seem like\N a trap but asking seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:11.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is all confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.23,0:18:15.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it. What was with that\N face she made a minute ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.28,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Other possibilities… Like an injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:25.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't seem like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:30.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't look like she's feeling\N too sick to exercise, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:35.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then that would leave… No…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:43.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not fair. Everyone's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:49.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I'm over here using all my brain\N power battling Такаги-сан in this heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката, are you taking this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.73,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I think you're just looking\N at the girls swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:58.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:00.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.85,0:19:04.62,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I heard boys look at girls' chests all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:06.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,I said I wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.84,0:19:11.17,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't say it out loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:15.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Такаги-сан doesn't really have a big chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:21.28,Main,Kimura,0,0,0,,I heard that a lot of small-chested girls\Nare pretty sensitive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:24.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's what the King of\NEarly Lunch, Kimura, said.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:30.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is Такаги-сан not swimming\N because she has a complex about her small chest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.68,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I knew it. You can't figure it out, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I win today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.01,0:19:38.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Такаги-сан, I know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:43.19,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You're concerned about\N your small chest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:50.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way I can say that! It's beyond rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.41,0:19:53.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the end, the only answer I have is "period."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:56.44,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's plenty rude, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:20:00.55,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,You're still thinking? You're almost out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:04.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it's even mentioned in the textbook.\N It's nothing to be embarrassed about!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:07.62,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, just say it with your head held high!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.93,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,The reason why you're sitting out\N the swimming lesson
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,is that…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,You're on your period.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:22.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:25.66,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,That's rude to say to a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.66,0:20:29.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,But it's mentioned in our\N textbook, and usually, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:34.87,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Нисиката, you're bright red.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:41.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then that would mean the reason is that\Nshe has a complex about her small chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Too funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:49.49,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Upsy-daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.93,0:21:00.11,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,By the way, "too embarrassed\N because of my small chest"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:04.26,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,is also incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.02,0:21:07.49,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,I changed my mind. May I swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:11.59,Main,Teacher,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:13.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:15.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then why was she watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.57,0:21:17.53,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Well then…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.53,0:21:21.17,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Now that I got to see Нисиката make\N a good face, I guess I'll go for a swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:25.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, you were staying out\Njust to tease me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,When your hand's all better…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.71,0:21:39.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,we can swim together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.79,0:21:50.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0,0,0,,Oh, it's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:22:00.38,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}When we do swim together,\N she's gonna tease me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:03.63,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the kind of person Такаги-сан is.
